msgid ""
"Because AI Agent Assembly is an **enforcement** control rather than a pure "
"observability or monitoring tool, the rows below span both categories: the "
"observability rows show that it still gives you the visibility those tools "
"provide, while the policy-enforcement, access-control, and "
"budget-enforcement rows show the security-checkpoint capabilities that "
"monitoring-only tools do not have. Read the matrix with that framing — equal "
"coverage on observability, decisive coverage on enforcement."
msgstr ""

